name: Portraits of a Darcy 2/16 - Darcy Got Back
description:
After bravely fighting off an entire mountain of Anacondas while dodging Caapi vines all the way down Darcy is back! Speculation is that Darcy manifested a quantum tunnel inside his based chakra to hasten his return while other people say he never really went anywhere. You can decide that for yourself!

2K digital loop & sound
